'''乔治·赫里奥特学校'''（George Heriot's School）是苏格兰[[爱丁堡|爱丁堡]]的一所[[独立学校_(英国)|独立学校]]，包括小学和中学，位于[[爱丁堡老城|爱丁堡老城]]的劳里斯顿坊（Lauriston Place），有超过1600名学生，155名教学人员和80名非教学工作人员。<ref>{{cite web|title=Facilities and Staff|url=http://www.george-heriots.com/school/facilities-staff|publisher=George Heriot's School|accessdate=2013-05-13|archive-date=2013-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719042153/http://www.george-heriots.com/school/facilities-staff|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 它创建于1628年，名为“乔治·赫里奥特慈善院”，根据皇家金匠乔治·赫里奥特的遗愿建立<ref>{{cite web|title=George Heriot and his Bequest|url=http://www.george-heriots.com/school/our-history/george-heriot-and-his-bequest|publisher=George Heriot's School|accessdate=2013-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512124552/http://www.george-heriots.com/school/our-history/george-heriot-and-his-bequest|archive-date=2017-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，并于1659年开学。

==建筑==
学校围绕一个大[[方庭|方庭]]，用[[砂岩|砂岩]]建造。<ref>{{cite web|title=Architectural Detail and Tower|url=http://www.george-heriots.com/school/our-history/architectural-detail-and-clock-tower|publisher=George Heriot's School|accessdate=13 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515064406/http://www.george-heriots.com/school/our-history/architectural-detail-and-clock-tower|archive-date=2017-05-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。学校的主楼为[[文艺复兴建筑|文艺复兴建筑]]，为威廉·华莱士的作品，直到他在1631年去世。<ref>{{cite book|last=Colvin|first=Howard|title=A Biographical Dictionary of British Architects 1600-1840|url=https://archive.org/details/biographicaldict0000colv|year=1978|publisher=John Murray}}</ref>继任者为威廉·艾图恩和John Mylne<ref>{{cite book|last=Colvin|first=Howard|title=A Biographical Dictionary of British Architects 1600-1840|url=https://archive.org/details/biographicaldict0000colv|year=1978|publisher=John Murray|pages=[https://archive.org/details/biographicaldict0000colv/page/569 569]–70}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=McWilliam|first=Colin|last2=Walker|first2=David|last3=Gifford|first3=John|title=The Buildings of Scotland: Edinburgh|year=1984|publisher=Penguin|pages=179–82}}</ref>。1676年，威廉布鲁斯爵士设计北立面的中央塔楼，最终于1693年完成。<ref name="buildings180">{{cite book|last=McWilliam|first=Colin|last2=Walker|first2=David|last3=Gifford|first3=John|title=The Buildings of Scotland: Edinburgh|year=1984|publisher=Penguin|page=180}}</ref>主楼是爱丁堡城墙外建造的第一个大型建筑。
